# PayIncus / Incudal ГўвӮ¬вҖқ Г©ВЎВ№Г§вҖәВ®Г§В»ЕёГӨВёвӮ¬ГЁВ§вҖһГ§ЕёВ©ГҜВјЛҶAGENTS.mdГҜВјвҖ°

> ГҰЕ“В¬ГҰвҖ“вҖЎГӨВ»В¶ГҰЛңВҜГҰЕ“В¬ГӨВ»вҖңГҘВәвҖң**ГҰвҖ°вӮ¬ГҰЕ“вҖ° AI agentГҜВјЛҶClaude CodeГЈвӮ¬ВҒcodex Г§ВӯвҖ°ГҜВјвҖ°Г§ЕЎвҖһГ§В»ЕёГӨВёвӮ¬ГҘВ·ВҘГӨВҪЕ“ГЁВ§вҖһГЁЕ’Ж’**ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
> `CLAUDE.md` Г©вӮ¬ЕЎГЁВҝвҖЎ `@AGENTS.md` ГҘВјвҖўГ§вҖқВЁГҰЕ“В¬ГҰвҖ“вҖЎГӨВ»В¶ ГўвӮ¬вҖқГўвӮ¬вҖқ Claude Code ГӨВёЕҪ codex ГЁВҜВ»ГҘЛҶВ°Г§ЕЎвҖһГҰЛңВҜ**ГҘВҗЕ’ГӨВёвӮ¬ГҘВҘвҖ”ГЁВ§вҖһГ§ЕёВ©**ГҜВјЕ’ГҰвҖқВ№ГЁВҝв„ўГӨВёвӮ¬ГӨВёВӘГҰвҖ“вҖЎГӨВ»В¶ГҘВҚВіГҘВҸВҜГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
> ГҰВқЖ’ГҘВЁВҒГЁВҝВҗГ§В»Вҙ/ГҘВҸвҖҳГ§вҖ°ЛҶГӨВәвҖ№ГҘВ®ЕҫГӨВ»ВҘГӨВ»вҖңГҘВәвҖңГҰВ В№Г§ЕЎвҖһ `OPERATIONS_HANDOFF.md`ГҜВјЛҶГҰвҖңВҚГӨВҪЕ“ГҰвҖ°вҖ№ГҘвҖ Е’ГҜВјвҖ°ГӨВёЕҪ `HANDOFF.md`ГҜВјЛҶГ§вҖ°ЛҶГҰЕ“В¬ГЁВҜВҒГҰВҚВ®ГҘВҸВ°ГЁВҙВҰГҜВјвҖ°ГӨВёВәГҘвҖЎвҖ ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ

---

## 0. ГҰВІЕёГ©вӮ¬ЕЎГЁВҜВӯГЁВЁвӮ¬
- ГӨВёЕҪ owner Г©В»ЛңГЁВ®ВӨГ§вҖқВЁ**ГӨВёВӯГҰвҖ“вҖЎ**ГҰВІЕёГ©вӮ¬ЕЎГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ

## 1. ГЁВҝв„ўГҰЛңВҜГӨВ»вӮ¬ГӨВ№ЛҶГ©ВЎВ№Г§вҖәВ®
**PayIncus**ГҜВјЛҶГҘвҖ вҖҰГ©Ж’ВЁГӨВ»ВЈГҘВҸВ· `incudal`ГҜВјвҖ°ГўвӮ¬вҖқГўвӮ¬вҖқГҘвҖўвҖ Г§вҖқВЁ IncusГҜВјЛҶLXC/KVMГҜВјвҖ°NAT VPS ГҘвҖқВ®ГҘВҚвҖ“ГӨВёЕҪГӨВәВӨГӨВ»ЛңГҘВ№ВіГҘВҸВ°ГҜВјЕ’**Г§ВәВҝГӨВёЕ ГЁВҝВҗГЁВҗВҘГӨВёВӯ**ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡГҘВҪвҖңГҘвҖ°ВҚГ§вҖқЕёГӨВәВ§Г§вҖ°ЛҶГҰЕ“В¬ **v1.3.7**ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡpnpm monorepoГҜВјЕЎ

| Г§вҖәВ®ГҘВҪвҖў | ГҰЕ вӮ¬ГҰЕ“ВҜГҰВ ЛҶ / ГӨВҪЕ“Г§вҖқВЁ |
|------|----------------|
| `client/` | Vue 3 + Vite SPAГЈвӮ¬вҖҡГҘВҸЕ’Г§В«ВҜГҰЕҫвҖһГҘВ»ВәГҜВјЛҶ`VITE_APP_ENTRY`ГҜВјвҖ°ГўвҖ вҖҷ `dist/user`ГҜВјЛҶpay.payincus.comГҜВјвҖ°+ `dist/admin`ГҜВјЛҶadmin.payincus.comГҜВјвҖ°ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡГӨВёВӨГ§В«ВҜГ§вҖ№В¬Г§В«вҖ№ГҰВәВҗГЈвӮ¬ВҒ**ГӨВёВҚГҘвҖҰВұГӨВәВ« cookie ГҘЕёЕё**ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ |
| `server/` | Fastify 5 + Prisma 7 + PostgreSQLГҜВјЕ’~300 TS ГҰвҖ“вҖЎГӨВ»В¶ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ~70 ГЁВ·ВҜГ§вҖқВұГЈвӮ¬ВҒ~15 ГЁВ°Ж’ГҘВәВҰ/workerГЈвӮ¬вҖҡГҰвҖ”В  RedisГҜВјЛҶГ§вҖқВЁ PG advisory lockГҜВјвҖ°ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡГӨВёвҖ°ГҘВҘвҖ”Г©вҖ°ВҙГҰВқЖ’Г©ВқВўГҜВјЕЎWeb Г§ЕЎвҖһ JWT+refresh cookieГЈвӮ¬ВҒPublic API Г§ЕЎвҖһ `pat_`/`poa_` tokenГЈвӮ¬ВҒhost agent Г§ЕЎвҖһ HMACГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ |
| `agent/` | Go ГҘВ®ВҝГӨВёВ» agentГҜВјЕ’ГҘВҸВӘГЁВҜВ»Г§вҖәвҖҳГҰЕҪВ§ГҜВјЛҶГҘВҝЖ’ГЁВ·Ві/ГЁВөвҖһГҰВәВҗ/ГҘВ®ЕҫГӨВҫвҖ№ГҰвӮ¬ВҒ/ГҰВөВҒГ©вҖЎВҸГҜВјвҖ°ГҜВјЕ’HMAC Г§ВӯВҫГҘВҗВҚГҜВјЕ’ГЁвҖЎВӘГҘВҚвҖЎГ§ВәВ§ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ |
| ГҘвҖҰВ¶ГҘВ®Ж’ | `docs-site/`ГҜВјЛҶVitePressГҜВјвҖ°ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`deploy/`ГҜВјЛҶsystemd+NginxГҜВјвҖ°ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`scripts/`ГҜВјЛҶГҘВ®вҖ°ГЁВЈвҖҰ/ГҰВ ВЎГ©ВӘЕ’/OTAГҜВјвҖ°ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`plugin-templates/`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`theme-templates/`ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ |

Г©Ж’ВЁГ§ВҪВІГҜВјЕЎГӨВёвҖ°ГҘВұвҖҡГҰвҖ№вҖ ГҘЛҶвҖ ГҜВјЛҶuser / admin / Г§В§ВҒГҰЕ“вҖ°ГҘВҗЕҪГ§В«ВҜ `127.0.0.1:3001`ГҜВјвҖ°ГҜВјЕ’ГЁВЈвҖҰГҰЕ“ВәГҰВ В№ `/opt/incudal`ГҜВјЕ’ГҘЕҪЕёГҘВӯВҗ OTAГҜВјЛҶ`releases/<ver-ts>` + `current` ГЁВҪВҜГ©вҖңВҫГҜВјвҖ°+ ГЁвҖЎВӘГҘЕ ВЁГҘвҖәЕҫГҰВ»ЕЎГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ

---

## 2. Г°ЕёвҖқВҙ Г§ВЎВ¬ГЁВ§вҖһГ§ЕёВ©ГҜВјЛҶГӨВёВҚГҘВҸВҜГҘВҚВҸГҘвҖўвҖ ГҜВјЕ’ГЁВҝВқГҘВҸВҚГҘВҚВіГӨВәвҖ№ГҰвҖўвҖҰГҜВјвҖ°

1. **ГӨВёВҚГ§ВўВ°Г§вҖқЕёГӨВәВ§**ГҜВјЕЎГҰЕ“ВӘГ§В»ВҸ owner ГҰЛңЕҪГ§ВЎВ®ГЁВҰВҒГҰВұвҖҡГҜВјЕ’**Г§В»ВқГӨВёВҚ** OTAГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҘВҸвҖҳГҘВёЖ’ГЈвӮ¬ВҒpushГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҰвҖ°вҖң tagГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҰвҖқВ№Г§вҖқЕёГӨВәВ§Г§ЕҪВҜГҘВўЖ’ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
2. **ГӨВёВҚГҘВҒЕЎГ§В ВҙГҘВқВҸГҰвӮ¬В§ git**ГҜВјЕЎГҰЕ“ВӘГ§В»ВҸ owner ГҰЛңЕҪГ§ВЎВ®ГЁВҰВҒГҰВұвҖҡГҜВјЕ’**Г§В»ВқГӨВёВҚ** `git reset`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`git checkout --`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҘВјВәГҘЛҶВ¶ГҘЛҶВ Г©в„ўВӨГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҰВёвҖҰГ§ВҗвҖ ГҰЕ“ВӘГЁВ·ЕёГЁВёВӘГҰвҖ“вҖЎГӨВ»В¶ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`git commit`/`git push`ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
3. **Г©В«ЛңГҘВҚВұГЁВ·ВҜГҘВҫвҖһГҘвҖҰЛҶГЁВҜВ»ГҘВҗЕҪГҘвҖ в„ў**ГҜВјЕЎГҰвҖқВ№ГҘЕ ВЁГӨВ»ВҘГӨВёвҖ№ГӨВ»В»ГӨВёвӮ¬Г©ВўвҖ ГҘЕёЕёГҜВјЕ’**ГҘВҝвҖҰГ©ВЎВ»ГҘвҖҰЛҶГЁВҜВ»Г§вҖәВёГҘвҖҰВіГӨВ»ВЈГ§В ВҒ + ГҘВҜВ№ГҘВәвҖқГҘВ®ЛҶГҘВҚВ«ГҰВөвҖ№ГЁВҜвҖў**ГҘвҖ ВҚГҘЕ ВЁГҰвҖ°вҖ№ГҜВјЕЎ
   > Г©вҖ°ВҙГҰВқЖ’ ГӮВ· ГҰвҖқВҜГӨВ»Лң ГӮВ· ГҰВқЖ’Г©в„ўВҗ ГӮВ· Г©ВЈЕҪГҰЕҪВ§ ГӮВ· ГЁВөвҖһГҰВәВҗГӨВәВӨГӨВ»Лң ГӮВ· ГҘвҖҰвҖҳГҰВҚВўГҰВөВҒГ§ВЁвҖ№ ГӮВ· ГҘВ®ЕҫГӨВҫвҖ№ГҘЛҶвҖәГҘВ»Вә ГӮВ· OTA
4. **ГҰвҖқВ№ГҘЕ ВЁГҰЕ“вӮ¬ГҘВ°ВҸГҘЕ’вҖ“**ГҜВјЕЎГӨВҝВ® bug / ГҘВҸвҖҳГ§вҖ°ЛҶГҰЕ“ЕёГ©вҖ”Вҙ**ГӨВёВҚГҘВҒЕЎГҘВӨВ§ГЁЕ’Ж’ГҘвҖәВҙГ©вҖЎВҚГҰЕҫвҖһ**ГҜВјЕ’ГҘВҸВӘГҰвҖқВ№ГҘВҝвҖҰГЁВҰВҒГ§ЕЎвҖһГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
5. **Г§В»ВқГӨВёВҚГҰВівҖһГҘВҜвҖ **ГҜВјЕЎГӨВ»В»ГӨВҪвҖў commitГЈвӮ¬ВҒhandoffГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҰвӮ¬В»Г§В»вҖңГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҰЛҶВӘГҘвҖәВҫГӨВёВӯГ©Ж’ВҪ**ГӨВёВҚГҘВҫвҖ”**ГҘвҖЎВәГ§ЕҪВ°ГҘвҖЎВӯГЁВҜВҒ / token / cookie / ГҘВҜвҖ Г©вҖҷВҘГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
6. **ГҰЕ“В¬ГҘЕ“В°ГЁВҝвҖЎ ГўвҖ°В  Г§вҖқЕёГӨВәВ§Г©ВӘЕ’ГЁВҜВҒ**ГҜВјЕЎГҰЕ“В¬ГҘЕ“В°Г©вӮ¬ЕЎГЁВҝвҖЎГЈвӮ¬ВҒGitHub ActionsГЈвӮ¬ВҒRelease ГЁВөвҖһГӨВәВ§ГЈвӮ¬ВҒOTAГЈвӮ¬ВҒГ§ВәВҝГӨВёЕ ГҘВ®ЕҫГЁВҜВҒГҰЛңВҜ**ГҘЛҶвҖ ГҘВјвӮ¬Г§ЕЎвҖһГЁВҜВҒГҰВҚВ®**ГҜВјЕ’ГӨВёВҚГҘВҸВҜГҰВ·В·ГӨВёВәГӨВёвӮ¬ГЁВ°ЛҶГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
7. **ГҰВҜВҸГҰВ¬ВЎГҰвҖқВ№ГҘЕ ВЁГҘВҝвҖҰГ©ВЎВ»ГЁВҝвҖЎГҘВҜВ№ГҘВәвҖқГҘВ®ЛҶГҘВҚВ«**ГҜВјЛҶГЁВ§ВҒ ГӮВ§4ГҜВјвҖ°ГҜВјЕ’ГҘВҗВҰГҘЛҶв„ўГЁВ§вҖ ГӨВёВә**ГҰЕ“ВӘГҘВ®Е’ГҰЛҶВҗ**ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
8. `RUN_DB_CHECKS=0 bash scripts/apply-online-update.sh <ver>` ГӨВјЕЎ**ГЁВ·ВіГЁВҝвҖЎ DB/ГҰвҖқВҜГӨВ»ЛңГҘВ°ВұГ§В»ВӘГҰВ ВЎГ©ВӘЕ’**ГҜВјЕ’ГӨВ»вҖҰГҘЕ“ВЁ owner ГҰЛңЕҪГ§ВЎВ®ГҰвҖ°В№ГҘвҖЎвҖ ГҰвҖ”В¶ГӨВҪВҝГ§вҖқВЁГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ

---

## 3. ГҰЕ“В¬ГҘЕ“В°ГҰвӮ¬ЕҪГӨВ№ЛҶГЁВ·вҖҳ

- **Г§ЕҪВҜГҘВўЖ’**ГҜВјЕЎNode ГўвҖ°ВҘ 20ГЈвӮ¬ВҒpnpm 9.14.2ГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҰЕ“В¬ГҘЕ“В° PostgreSQL 16ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
- **ГЁВЈвҖҰГӨВҫВқГЁВөвҖ“**ГҜВјЕЎ`pnpm install`
- **ГӨВёвӮ¬ГҰЕ Е ГЁВөВ·ГҘвҖҰВЁГ©Ж’ВЁГҜВјЛҶserver + user + adminГҜВјвҖ°**ГҜВјЕЎ`pnpm dev`
- **ГҘЛҶвҖ ГҘВјвӮ¬ГЁВөВ·**ГҜВјЕЎ
  - ГҘВҗЕҪГ§В«ВҜГҜВјЕЎ`NODE_ENV=development JWT_SECRET=dev-secret-12345678 HOST=127.0.0.1 PORT=3001 pnpm --filter server exec tsx watch src/app.ts`
  - Г§вҖқВЁГҰЛҶВ·ГҘвҖ°ВҚГ§В«ВҜГҜВјЕЎ`pnpm dev:user`
  - Г§В®ВЎГ§ВҗвҖ ГҘвҖ°ВҚГ§В«ВҜГҜВјЕЎ`pnpm dev:admin`
- **Г§В«ВҜГҘВҸВЈ**ГҜВјЕЎГҘВҗЕҪГ§В«ВҜ API **3001** ГӮВ· Г§вҖқВЁГҰЛҶВ·ГҘвҖ°ВҚГ§В«ВҜ **3000** ГӮВ· Г§В®ВЎГ§ВҗвҖ ГҘвҖ°ВҚГ§В«ВҜ **3002**ГҜВјЛҶГҘвҖ°ВҚГ§В«ВҜ dev Г§В»ВҸ proxy ГҰвҖ°вҖңГҘЛҶВ° 3001ГҜВјвҖ°ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ

---

## 4. Г°ЕёвҖәВЎГҜВёВҸ ГҘВ®ЛҶГҘВҚВ«ГҰВөвҖ№ГЁВҜвҖўГ§ВәВӘГҘВҫвҖ№ГҜВјЛҶГҰЕ“В¬ГӨВ»вҖңГҘВәвҖңГ§ЕЎвҖһГҘвҖҳВҪГ©вҖ”ВЁГҜВјвҖ°

`server/package.json` Г©вҖЎЕ’ГҰЕ“вҖ° **200+ ГӨВёВӘГ§вҖ№В¬Г§В«вҖ№ `test-*-guards.ts`**ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡГҘВ®Ж’ГӨВ»В¬ГҰЕ Е ГҘвҖҰВіГ©вҖқВ®ГӨВёЕЎГҘЕ ВЎ/ГҘвҖ°ВҚГ§В«ВҜГ§В»вҖңГҰЕҫвҖһГўвӮ¬Е“Г©вҖҷвҖ°ГҰВӯВ»ГўвӮ¬ВқГҜВјЕ’`pnpm test` ГӨВјЕЎГЁВ·вҖҳГҘвҖҰВЁГҘВҘвҖ”ГҜВјЛҶclient+server type-check + ГҘвҖҰВЁГ©Ж’ВЁГҘВ®ЛҶГҘВҚВ«ГҜВјвҖ°ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ**ГӨВ»В»ГӨВҪвҖўГҰвҖқВ№ГҘЕ ВЁГҘВҝвҖҰГ©ВЎВ»ГЁВ®В©Г§вҖәВёГҘвҖҰВіГҘВ®ЛҶГҘВҚВ«Г©вӮ¬ЕЎГЁВҝвҖЎГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ**

- **ГҘвҖҰВЁГ©вҖЎВҸ**ГҜВјЛҶГҰвҖҰВўГҜВјЕ’ГҘВҸвҖҳГ§вҖ°ЛҶГҘвҖ°ВҚГЁВ·вҖҳГҜВјвҖ°ГҜВјЕЎ`pnpm test`
- **ГҘВҚвҖўГӨВёВӘ**ГҜВјЕЎ`pnpm --filter server test:<guard-name>`
- **ГҘвҖ°ВҚГ§В«ВҜГҰЕ“вӮ¬ГҘВёВёГ§вҖқВЁГӨВёвҖ°ГӨВёВӘ**ГҜВјЕЎ
  - `test:frontend-route-guards` ГўвӮ¬вҖқГўвӮ¬вҖқ ГЁВ·ВҜГ§вҖқВұ / **ГЁВЎВЁГҰВ ВјГҘВёЖ’ГҘВұвӮ¬** / `@click` ГЁВ·ВҜГҘВҫвҖһГҰвҖ“ВӯГЁВЁвӮ¬
  - `test:frontend-dist-boundary-guards` ГўвӮ¬вҖқГўвӮ¬вҖқ ГҘВҸЕ’Г§В«ВҜ dist ГЁВҫВ№Г§вҖўЕ’
  - `test:frontend-i18n-keys` ГўвӮ¬вҖқГўвӮ¬вҖқ i18n key ГҘВ®Е’ГҰвҖўВҙГҰвӮ¬В§
- **Go agent**ГҜВјЕЎ`pnpm test:agent`

### ГўЕЎВ ГҜВёВҸ ГЁВЎВЁГҰВ ВјГҘВёЖ’ГҘВұвӮ¬ГҘВ®ЛҶГҘВҚВ«ГҜВјЛҶГҰЕ“вӮ¬ГҘВ®В№ГҰЛңвҖңГЁВёВ©Г©вҖәВ·ГҜВјвҖ°
ГӨВёвӮ¬ГҰвҖ°В№ГЁВЎВЁГЁВўВ«ГҘВ®ЛҶГҘВҚВ«**Г©вҖқВҒГҘВ®ЕЎ**ГӨВёВәГўвӮ¬Е“**Г§В§В»ГҘЕ ВЁГҘВҚВЎ + PC ГҘВ®ЕЎГҘВ®ВҪГЁВЎВЁГҜВјЛҶ`table-fixed` / `overflow-hidden`ГҜВјвҖ°ГҜВјЕ’Г§В»ВқГӨВёВҚГҰВЁВӘГҘВҗвҖҳГҰВ»ЕЎГҘЕ ВЁ**ГўвӮ¬ВқГҜВјЕ’ГҘВ№В¶**ГҘВҸВҚГҘВҗвҖҳГ§ВҰВҒГҰВӯВў** `overflow-x-auto` / `min-w-[...]` / ГҘЕҪВ»ГҰЕҪвҖ° `table-fixed`ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
- ГҰЖ’ВіГӨВҝВ®ГўвӮ¬Е“ГҘВ®ВҪГЁВЎВЁГҰЕ’ВӨГҘЕҪвҖ№ГўвӮ¬ВқГҰвҖ”В¶ГҜВјЕЎ**ГҘвҖҰЛҶГҘЛҶВӨГҰвҖ“ВӯГЁВҜВҘГЁВЎВЁГҰЛңВҜГҘВҗВҰГҘЕ“ВЁГҘВ®ЛҶГҘВҚВ«ГҰВёвҖҰГҘВҚвҖўГ©вҖЎЕ’**ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡГ©вҖқВҒГҘВ®ЕЎГЁВЎВЁ**ГҘВҸВӘГЁЖ’ВҪГҘЕ“ВЁ `table-fixed` ГҘвҖ вҖҰГҘВ№ВіГЁВЎВЎГҘЛҶвҖ”ГҘВ®ВҪ**ГҜВјЛҶГҘЛҶвҖ”ГҘВ®ВҪГ§в„ўВҫГҘЛҶвҖ ГҰВҜвҖқГҘВҗЛҶГЁВ®ВЎ = 100%ГҜВјвҖ°+ ГҘвҖҰВҒГЁВ®ВёГҘВҚвҖўГҘвҖҰЖ’ГҰВ ВјГҰВҚВўГЁВЎЕ’ + Г©ВқВ Г§В§В»ГҘЕ ВЁГҘВҚВЎГҘВәвҖқГҘВҜВ№Г§ВӘвҖһГҘВұВҸГҜВјвҖә**ГӨВёВҚГЁЖ’ВҪ**ГҰвҖқВ№ГҰЛҶВҗГҰВЁВӘГҘВҗвҖҳГҰВ»ЕЎГҘЕ ВЁГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
- ГҘВҸвҖ”Г©вҖқВҒГҘВ®ЕЎГ§ЕЎвҖһГЁВЎВЁГҜВјЛҶГ§вҖқВЁГҰЛҶВ·Г§В«ВҜГҜВјвҖ°ГҜВјЕЎ`MyPackagesView`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`MyHostsView`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`TransfersView`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`OrdersView`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`InvitesView`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`FlashSalesView`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`HostingWalletView`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`InstancesView`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`LogsView`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`EntertainmentView`ГҜВјвҖәГҜВјЛҶГ§В®ВЎГ§ВҗвҖ Г§В«ВҜГҜВјвҖ°`admin/BillingView`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`admin/ImagesView`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`admin/HelpManageView`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`admin/MailView`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`admin/PluginCenterView`ГҜВјвҖәГҜВјЛҶГ§В»вҖһГӨВ»В¶ГҜВјвҖ°`HostPublicIpv4Tab`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`InstanceLogsTab`ГЈвӮ¬ВҒ`ConfigEditModal`ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
- ГҰвҖқВ№ГӨВ»В»ГӨВёвӮ¬ГҘвҖ°ВҚГ§В«ВҜГҰвҖ“вҖЎГӨВ»В¶ГҘВҗЕҪ**ГҘВҝвҖҰГЁВ·вҖҳ** `test:frontend-route-guards`ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ

---

## 5. ГҰЕҫвҖһГҘВ»Вә / ГҰВ ВЎГ©ВӘЕ’ГҘвҖҳВҪГӨВ»ВӨ

| Г§вҖәВ®Г§ЕЎвҖһ | ГҘвҖҳВҪГӨВ»ВӨ |
|------|------|
| ГҰЕҫвҖһГҘВ»ВәГҜВјЛҶГҘВҗВ« dist ГЁВҫВ№Г§вҖўЕ’ГҘВ®ЛҶГҘВҚВ«ГҜВјвҖ°| `pnpm build` |
| ГҘВҸВӘГҰЕҫвҖһГҘВ»ВәГҘвҖ°ВҚГ§В«ВҜ / ГҘВҗЕҪГ§В«ВҜ | `pnpm build:client` / `pnpm build:server` |
| LintГҜВјЛҶГҰВЈвӮ¬ГҰЕёВҘ / ГЁвҖЎВӘГҘЕ ВЁГӨВҝВ®ГҜВјвҖ°| `pnpm lint` / `pnpm lint:fix` |
| Г§ВұВ»ГҘЕҫвҖ№ГҰВЈвӮ¬ГҰЕёВҘ | `pnpm --filter client type-check` ГӮВ· `pnpm --filter server type-check` |
| ГҘвҖҰВЁГҘВҘвҖ”ГҘВ®ЛҶГҘВҚВ« | `pnpm test` |
| ГҰвҖ“вҖЎГҰВЎВЈГ§В«в„ўГҘВјвӮ¬ГҘВҸвҖҳ / ГҰЕҫвҖһГҘВ»Вә | `pnpm docs:dev` / `pnpm docs:build` |

---

## 6. UI ГҰвҖқВ№ГҘЕ ВЁГ§ВәВҰГҰВқЕёГҜВјЛҶГҘВҚвҖўГЁвҖ°ВІГ©вҖЎВҚГҘВҒЕЎГЁВҝвҖәГЁВЎЕ’ГӨВёВӯГҜВјвҖ°

- **ГҰвҖ“В№ГҘВҗвҖҳ**ГҜВјЕЎГЁвҖ№В№ГҰЕҫЕ“ГҘВјВҸ**Г§ВәВҜГ©В»вҖҳГ§в„ўВҪГҘВҚвҖўГЁвҖ°ВІ**ГҜВјЛҶГҰВөвҖҰГЁвҖ°ВІ=Г§в„ўВҪГҘВәвҖўГ©В»вҖҳГҘВӯвҖ”ГҜВјЕ’ГҰВ·ВұГЁвҖ°ВІ=Г©В»вҖҳГҘВәвҖўГ§в„ўВҪГҘВӯвҖ”ГҜВјвҖ°ГҜВјЕ’ГҘЕҪВ»ГӨВәЕ’ГҰВ¬ВЎГҘвҖҰЖ’/ГҘВҗвҖ°Г§ВҘВҘГ§вҖ°В©/Г§В«вҖ№Г§В»ЛңГЈвӮ¬вҖҡГ§Е В¶ГҰвӮ¬ВҒГЁвҖ°ВІ**ГҘВҸВӘГӨВҝВқГ§вҖўв„ўГ§В»Вҝ/Г§ВҗВҘГ§ВҸвӮ¬/Г§ВәВў**ГӨВёвҖ°Г§В§ВҚГҜВјЛҶГЁВҝВҗГЁВЎЕ’/ГҘВҫвҖҰГҘВӨвҖһГ§ВҗвҖ /ГҘВӨВұГЁВҙВҘГҜВјвҖ°ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
- **Г§ВәВўГ§ВәВҝ**ГҜВјЕЎГҘВҸВӘГҰвҖқВ№**ГҰВ В·ГҘВјВҸ / ГҘВёЖ’ГҘВұвӮ¬ / ГҰвҖ“вҖЎГҰВЎЛҶГҘВұвҖҡГ§ВәВ§**ГҜВјЕ’**ГӨВёВҚГ§ВўВ°**ГҘВҗЕҪГ§В«ВҜГҰЕҪВҘГҘВҸВЈГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҰВқЖ’Г©в„ўВҗГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҰвҖқВҜГӨВ»Лң/ГЁВ®ВўГҘВҚвҖў/ГҘВ®ЕҫГӨВҫвҖ№ГҘЛҶвҖәГҘВ»Вә/OTA Г§ВӯвҖ°ГӨВёЕЎГҘЕ ВЎГ©вӮ¬В»ГЁВҫвҖҳГӨВёЕҪГЁВ·ВҜГ§вҖқВұГЁВЎЕ’ГӨВёВәГўвӮ¬вҖқГўвӮ¬вҖқ**ГҘЕ ЕёГЁЖ’ВҪ 100% ГӨВёВҚГҘВҸЛң**ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
- **Г©вҖҰВҚГЁвҖ°ВІГЁВөВ° token ГҘВұвҖҡ**ГҜВјЛҶ`client/tailwind.config.js`ГҜВјвҖ°ГҜВјЕЎГӨВёвӮ¬ГҘВ вҖ ГҘВҪВ©ГЁвҖ°ВІ ramp ГҘВ·ВІГҰЛңВ ГҘВ°вҖһГҘЛҶВ°ГӨВёВӯГҰвӮ¬В§Г§ВҒВ°ГҜВјвҖә`rose ГўвҖ вҖҷ Г§Е“ЕёГ§ВәВў`ГҜВјЛҶГҘВҚВұГ©в„ўВ©/ГӨВәВҸГҰВҚЕёГЁВҜВӯГӨВ№вҖ°ГҜВјвҖ°**ГӨВҝВқГ§вҖўв„ўГӨВёВҚГҘВҸВҜГ§ВҒВ°ГҘЕ’вҖ“**ГҜВјвҖәГҰВёВёГҰЛҶВҸГҘЕ’вҖ“ГҰВЁВЎГҘВқвҖ”ГҜВјЛҶГҰЛҶВҗГҘВ°Вұ/Г§ВӯВҫГҘЛҶВ°/ГҰЕ ВҪГҘВҘвҖ“/Г§ВЁвӮ¬ГҰЕ“вҖ°ГҘВәВҰГҜВјвҖ°ГҘВҪВ©ГЁвҖ°ВІ**ГҘЛҶВ»ГҰвҖһВҸГӨВҝВқГ§вҖўв„ў**ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
- `kawaii-cloud.css` **ГҰВёВҗГЁВҝвҖәГҰвҖқВ№Г©вӮ¬В ГЈвӮ¬ВҒГӨВёВҚГ©вҖЎВҚГҘвҖ в„ў**ГҜВјвҖәГҘВҚвҖўГ©ВЎВөГҘЕҪВ»ГЁвҖ°ВІГ§вҖқВЁГ©ВЎВөГ©ВқВў `<style scoped>`ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
- ГҘЕ ВЁГҰвҖўЛҶГҘВҸВҜГ§вҖқВЁ **GSAP**ГҜВјЛҶГҘВ·ВІГЁВЈвҖҰ gsap-skillsГҜВјЕ’ГЁВ§ВҒ `.claude/skills/`ГҜВјвҖ°ГҜВјвҖәГҘВ°Е Г©вҖЎВҚ `prefers-reduced-motion`ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ

---

## 7. ГҘВҚВҸГӨВҪЕ“ГҰВЁВЎГҘЕҫвҖ№ГҜВјЛҶClaude Code ГўвҖЎвҖһ codexГҜВјвҖ°

- **Claude Code = ГҰЕ вӮ¬ГҰЕ“ВҜГЁВҙЕёГЁВҙВЈГӨВәВә / Г©вҖәвҖ ГҰЛҶВҗГҰвҖ“В№**ГҜВјЕЎГҘВ®ЕЎГҰВ В№ГҘвҖәВ ГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҘЛҶвҖЎГӨВ»В»ГҘЕ ВЎГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҘвҖ в„ўГЁВ§вҖһГҰВ ВјГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҘВ®ЛҶГӨВёВҚГҘВҸЛңГ©вҖЎВҸГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҘВ®ВЎ diffГЈвӮ¬ВҒГЁВ·вҖҳГҘВ®ЛҶГҘВҚВ«ГЈвӮ¬ВҒГ§Е“ЕёГҰЕ“ВәГ©ВӘЕ’ГЁВҜВҒГЈвӮ¬ВҒГ§В®ВЎ gitГҜВјЛҶ**ГӨВ»вҖҰГҘЕ“ВЁ owner ГҘВҗЕ’ГҰвҖһВҸГҰвҖ”В¶** commit / pushГҜВјвҖ°ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
- **codex = ГҘВ®ЕҫГ§ЕҪВ°ГҘВ·ВҘГӨВәВә**ГҜВјЕЎГҰЕ’вҖ° Claude Г§В»в„ўГ§ЕЎвҖһГЁВ§вҖһГҰВ ВјГҘВ®ЕҫГ§ЕҪВ°ГҰвҖқВ№ГҘЕ ВЁГҜВјЕ’ГҘВ°ВӨГҘвҖҰВ¶**ГӨВҪЕҪ/ГӨВёВӯГҘВҚВұГЈвӮ¬ВҒГЁвҖЎВӘГҘЕ’вҖҰГҘВҗВ«ГЈвӮ¬ВҒГҘВҸВҜГҘВ№В¶ГЁВЎЕ’**Г§ЕЎвҖһГҘВқвҖ”ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
- **Г©ВЈЕҪГ©в„ўВ©ГҘЛҶвҖ ГҰВЎВЈ**ГҜВјЕЎГ©В«ЛңГҘВҚВұГЁВ·ВҜГҘВҫвҖһГ§вҖқВұ Claude ГҘВ®ЕЎГҰВ В№ГҘвҖәВ  + ГҰвҖқВ¶Г§ВҙВ§ГЁВ§вҖһГҰВ ВјГҜВјвҖәГӨВҪЕҪ/ГӨВёВӯГҘВҚВұ codex ГҘВҸВҜГ§В«ВҜГҘЛҶВ°Г§В«ВҜГӨВҝВ®ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ**ГӨВ»В»ГӨВҪвҖўГӨВёвӮ¬ГҰвҖ“В№ГҰвҖқВ№ГҘВ®Е’Г©Ж’ВҪГЁВҰВҒГЁВ·вҖҳГ§вҖәВёГҘвҖҰВіГҘВ®ЛҶГҘВҚВ«ГҜВјЕ’Claude Г§В»ЕёГӨВёвӮ¬ГҘВ®ВЎГҰЕёВҘГҘВҗЕҪГҰвҖ°ВҚГЁВҝвҖәГҘвҖҰВҘГӨВёвҖ№ГӨВёвӮ¬ГҰВӯВҘГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ**
- **Г©ВҒВҝГҘвҖҰВҚГҘвҖ ВІГ§ВӘВҒ**ГҜВјЕЎГҘВҗЕ’ГӨВёвӮ¬ГҰвҖ°В№ГҰвҖ“вҖЎГӨВ»В¶ГӨВёвӮ¬ГҰВ¬ВЎГҘВҸВӘГЁВ®В©ГӨВёвӮ¬ГӨВёВӘ agent ГҰвҖқВ№ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ

---

## 8. ГӨВёвӮ¬ГӨВёВӘГҰвҖқВ№ГҘЕ ВЁГ§ЕЎвҖһГЈвӮ¬Е’ГҘВ®Е’ГҰЛҶВҗГЈвӮ¬ВҚГҘВ®ЕЎГӨВ№вҖ°

1. Г§вҖәВёГҘвҖҰВі **type-check** Г©вӮ¬ЕЎГЁВҝвҖЎГҜВјвҖә
2. Г§вҖәВёГҘвҖҰВі **ГҘВ®ЛҶГҘВҚВ«ГҰВөвҖ№ГЁВҜвҖў** Г©вӮ¬ЕЎГЁВҝвҖЎГҜВјвҖә
3. ГЁвҖ№ВҘГҘЕ ВЁГҘвҖ°ВҚГ§В«ВҜ ГўвҖ вҖҷ **ГҘВҸЕ’Г§В«ВҜ build** Г©вӮ¬ЕЎГЁВҝвҖЎГҜВјвҖә
4. **Г§Е“ЕёГҰЕ“ВәГЁВ·вҖҳГЁВҝвҖЎ**ГҘВҸвҖ”ГҘВҪВұГҘвҖңВҚГҰВөВҒГ§ВЁвҖ№ГҜВјЛҶГӨВёВҚГҰЛңВҜГҘВҸВӘГ§Е“вҖ№ГҰВөвҖ№ГЁВҜвҖўГҜВјвҖ°ГҜВјвҖә
5. **ГҰЕ ВҘГҘвҖҳЕ **ГҜВјЕЎГҰвҖқВ№ГӨВәвҖ ГҘвҖңВӘГӨВәвҖәГҰвҖ“вҖЎГӨВ»В¶ / ГӨВёВәГӨВ»вӮ¬ГӨВ№ЛҶ / Г©ВЈЕҪГ©в„ўВ© / ГҰвӮ¬ЕҪГӨВ№ЛҶГ©ВӘЕ’ГЁВҜВҒГ§ЕЎвҖһГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ

ГӨВ»ВҘГӨВёЕ ГӨВ»В»ГӨВёвӮ¬ГҰЕ“ВӘГҰВ»ВЎГЁВ¶Ві = **ГҰЕ“ВӘГҘВ®Е’ГҰЛҶВҗ**ГЈвӮ¬вҖҡ
import assert from 'node:assert/strict'
import { readFileSync } from 'node:fs'
import { resolve } from 'node:path'

const routeSource = readFileSync(resolve(process.cwd(), 'src/routes/system-config.ts'), 'utf8')

assert.ok(
  routeSource.includes('const positiveIntegerConfigPattern = /^[1-9]\\d*$/') &&
    routeSource.includes('const nonNegativeIntegerConfigPattern = /^(?:0|[1-9]\\d*)$/') &&
    routeSource.includes('function parsePositiveConfigInteger(value: string, max = Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER): number | null') &&
    routeSource.includes('function parseNonNegativeConfigInteger(value: string, max = Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER): number | null') &&
    routeSource.includes('function parseDecimalMoneyConfig(value: string, max: number): number | null'),
  'system config route must define strict string-to-number config parsers'
)

assert.ok(
  routeSource.includes('const packageId = parsePositiveConfigInteger(popupPromoPackageId, 2147483647)') &&
    routeSource.includes('const packageId = parsePositiveConfigInteger(config.value, 2147483647)') &&
    routeSource.includes('config.value = packageId.toString()'),
  'popup promo package config must reject non-decimal, unsafe, and missing package IDs before lookup/persistence'
)

assert.ok(
  routeSource.includes("if (typeof amount !== 'number' || !Number.isFinite(amount) || amount < 0)") &&
    routeSource.includes("resource === 'balance' && amount > maxRegisterGiftBalance") &&
    routeSource.includes("resource === 'points' && (!Number.isSafeInteger(amount) || amount > maxRegisterGiftPoints)") &&
    routeSource.includes('config.value = serializeInviteCostOptions(options)'),
  'invite generation cost config must require JSON numbers and bounded balance/points amounts'
)

assert.ok(
  routeSource.includes('const num = parseDecimalMoneyConfig(config.value, maxRegisterGiftBalance)') &&
    routeSource.includes("config.key === 'smtp_port'") &&
    routeSource.includes('? 65535') &&
    routeSource.includes('const num = parseNonNegativeConfigInteger(config.value, max)') &&
    routeSource.includes("config.key === 'telegram_group_invite_expire_minutes' || config.key === 'telegram_vip_group_invite_expire_minutes'") &&
    routeSource.includes("config.key === 'invite_default_expire_days' && num > 3650"),
  'system config numeric keys must reject scientific notation, unsafe integers, and out-of-range values'
)

for (const forbiddenPattern of [
  'const packageId = Number(popupPromoPackageId)',
  'const packageId = Number(config.value)',
  'const amount = Number((item as { amount?: unknown }).amount)',
  'const num = Number(config.value)',
  'isNaN(num)'
]) {
  assert.ok(
    !routeSource.includes(forbiddenPattern),
    `system config route must not keep loose numeric coercion: ${forbiddenPattern}`
  )
}

assert.ok(
  routeSource.includes("const value = config.value.trim()") &&
    routeSource.includes('!decimalMoneyPattern.test(value)') &&
    routeSource.includes('num > maxTransferFee'),
  'transfer fee must keep strict two-decimal money validation and explicit maximum'
)

const sensitiveKeysStart = routeSource.indexOf('const sensitiveKeys = [')
assert.notEqual(sensitiveKeysStart, -1, 'system config route must define audit-log sensitive keys')
const sensitiveKeysEnd = routeSource.indexOf(']', sensitiveKeysStart)
assert.notEqual(sensitiveKeysEnd, -1, 'system config audit-log sensitive keys section must be closed')
const sensitiveKeysSection = routeSource.slice(sensitiveKeysStart, sensitiveKeysEnd)
assert.ok(
  sensitiveKeysSection.includes("'telegram_group_chat_id'") &&
    sensitiveKeysSection.includes("'telegram_vip_group_chat_id'"),
  'system config audit logging must redact Telegram group chat IDs'
)

console.log('system config value guard tests passed')
import assert from 'node:assert/strict'
import { readFileSync } from 'node:fs'
import { resolve } from 'node:path'

const repoRoot = resolve(import.meta.dirname, '../..')

function read(path: string): string {
  return readFileSync(resolve(repoRoot, path), 'utf8')
}

const serverApp = read('server/src/app.ts')
const route = read('server/src/routes/system-update.ts')
const versionLib = read('server/src/lib/system-version.ts')
const prismaSchema = read('server/prisma/schema.prisma')
const migration = read('server/prisma/migrations/20260623093000_add_system_update_tasks/migration.sql')
const adminApi = read('client/src/api/admin.ts')
const userApi = read('client/src/api/index.ts')
const adminRouter = read('client/src/router/admin.ts')
const adminNav = read('client/src/config/side-nav-items-admin.ts')
const releaseWorkflow = read('.github/workflows/release.yml')
const onlineScript = read('scripts/apply-online-update.sh')
const atomicMigrationScript = read('scripts/migrate-ota-atomic-layout.sh')
const installPanel = read('scripts/install-panel.sh')
const backendService = read('deploy/incudal-backend.service.example')
const updateService = read('deploy/incudal-online-update@.service.example')
const rollbackService = read('deploy/incudal-online-rollback@.service.example')
const runTask = read('server/src/scripts/run-system-update-task.ts')
const rollbackTask = read('server/src/scripts/rollback-system-update-task.ts')
const systemUpdateTasksDb = read('server/src/db/system-update-tasks.ts')
const rootPackage = read('package.json')
const serverPackage = read('server/package.json')

assert.ok(
  serverApp.includes("import systemUpdateRoutes from './routes/system-update.js'") &&
    serverApp.includes("fastify.register(systemUpdateRoutes, { prefix: '/api/admin/system-update' })"),
  'system update routes must be mounted only under the admin API namespace'
)

assert.ok(
  route.includes('onRequest: [fastify.authenticateAdmin]') &&
    route.includes('SUPER_ADMIN_REQUIRED') &&
    route.includes("return user.username === 'admin'") &&
    route.includes('SYSTEM_UPDATE_ALLOWED_ADMIN_IDS'),
  'system update routes must require admin authentication plus super-admin gating'
)

assert.ok(
  versionLib.includes('const tagPattern = /^v\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+') &&
    versionLib.includes('repositoryAvailable: false') &&
    versionLib.includes("rev-parse', '--is-inside-work-tree") &&
    versionLib.includes('interface GitHubReleaseAsset') &&
    versionLib.includes('getOtaReleaseInfo') &&
    versionLib.includes('ota-manifest.json') &&
    versionLib.includes('SYSTEM_UPDATE_RELEASE_REPOSITORY') &&
    route.includes('isValidReleaseTag(targetVersion)') &&
    route.includes('GIT_REPOSITORY_REQUIRED') &&
    route.includes('additionalProperties: false'),
  'system update must only accept controlled release tags, require a Git checkout, expose OTA manifest metadata, and reject extra input'
)

assert.ok(
  versionLib.includes('const latest = tags[0] ? await buildAvailableUpdate(tags[0]) : null') &&
    versionLib.includes('updates.push(latest?.version === tag ? latest : await buildAvailableUpdate(tag))') &&
    versionLib.includes('latest,') &&
    versionLib.includes('updateAvailable: updates.length > 0') &&
    route.includes('canManageUpdates: await canManageSystemUpdates(getRequestUser(request))') &&
    route.includes("fastify.post<{ Body: StartUpdateBody }>('/start'") &&
    route.includes('if (!(await requireUpdateManager(request, reply))) return'),
  'system update checks must always expose the newest release tag while keeping updateAvailable and mutation permissions separate'
)

assert.ok(
  prismaSchema.includes('model SystemUpdateTask') &&
    prismaSchema.includes('enum SystemUpdateTaskStatus') &&
    migration.includes('CREATE TABLE "system_update_tasks"') &&
    migration.includes('FOREIGN KEY ("started_by_user_id") REFERENCES "users"("id")'),
  'system update tasks must be persisted with an audited admin user'
)

assert.ok(
  adminApi.includes('/admin/system-update/version') &&
    adminApi.includes('/admin/system-update/start') &&
    adminRouter.includes("path: '/admin/system-update'") &&
    adminNav.includes("path: '/admin/system-update'"),
  'admin frontend must expose the version update page and API client'
)

assert.ok(
  !userApi.includes('/admin/system-update') &&
    !userApi.includes('systemUpdate'),
  'customer API bundle must not expose system update endpoints'
)

assert.ok(
  runTask.includes("git', ['checkout', '--force', targetVersion]") &&
    runTask.includes("git', ['clean', '-fdx'") &&
    runTask.includes("'-e', '.env'") &&
    runTask.includes("'-e', '.gitconfig'") &&
    runTask.includes("git', ['config', '--global', '--add', 'safe.directory', appDir]") &&
    runTask.includes("targetVersion = task.targetVersion") &&
    runTask.includes("pnpm', ['build']") &&
    runTask.includes("test:frontend-dist-boundary-guards") &&
    runTask.includes("test:frontend-route-guards") &&
    runTask.includes("systemctl', ['restart', serviceName]") &&
    runTask.includes('waitForBackendHealth()') &&
    runTask.includes("verify:production") &&
    runTask.includes("verify:log-header") &&
    runTask.includes("smoke:agent-release") &&
    runTask.includes("tryMarkSystemUpdateTaskRunning(taskId, ['pending'], logPath)") &&
    runTask.includes('already claimed or finished; skipping duplicate worker') &&
    runTask.includes('await closePrismaDatabase()'),
  'online updater must build, migrate, guard, restart, and verify before marking success'
)

assert.ok(
  systemUpdateTasksDb.includes('export async function tryMarkSystemUpdateTaskRunning') &&
    systemUpdateTasksDb.includes('updateMany({') &&
    systemUpdateTasksDb.includes('status: { in: allowedStatuses }') &&
    systemUpdateTasksDb.includes('return result.count === 1') &&
    rollbackTask.includes("tryMarkSystemUpdateTaskRunning(taskId, ['success', 'failed'], logPath)") &&
    rollbackTask.includes('already claimed or not rollbackable; skipping duplicate worker') &&
    rollbackTask.includes('await closePrismaDatabase()'),
  'online update and rollback workers must atomically claim tasks before touching staging, downloads, releases, or rollback paths'
)

assert.ok(
  runTask.includes('SYSTEM_UPDATE_APPLY_MODE') &&
    runTask.includes('getOtaReleaseInfo(targetVersion)') &&
    runTask.includes('selectRuntimeArtifact') &&
    runTask.includes('downloadArtifact') &&
    runTask.includes('createHash') &&
    runTask.includes('OTA artifact sha256 mismatch') &&
    runTask.includes("tar', ['-xzf', artifactPath") &&
    runTask.includes('assertArtifactStaging') &&
    runTask.includes("'.git'") &&
    runTask.includes('No usable OTA artifact found; falling back to Git build mode') &&
    runTask.includes('Skipping source-based Agent release smoke in artifact mode') &&
    runTask.includes('autoRollbackFromBackup') &&
    runTask.includes('switchCurrentRelease') &&
    runTask.includes('applyArtifactAtomic') &&
    runTask.includes('function deriveInstallDir') &&
    runTask.includes("resolvedAppDir.endsWith('/current')") &&
    runTask.includes("releasesDir.endsWith('/releases')") &&
    runTask.includes("join(installDir, '.incudal-update-downloads')") &&
    runTask.includes("join(installDir, 'current')") &&
    runTask.includes("join(installDir, 'releases')") &&
    runTask.includes('SYSTEM_UPDATE_MIN_FREE_MB') &&
    runTask.includes('SYSTEM_UPDATE_RELEASES_KEEP') &&
    runTask.includes('SYSTEM_UPDATE_BACKUP_TASKS_KEEP') &&
    runTask.includes('assertRequiredCommands()') &&
    runTask.includes('defaultExecutionPath') &&
    runTask.includes("PATH: executionPath") &&
    runTask.includes("cleanupUpdateDownloadDir('ГҰвҖәВҙГҰвҖ“В°ГҘВјвӮ¬ГҘВ§вҖ№ГҘвҖ°ВҚ')") &&
    runTask.includes('assertEnoughDiskSpace') &&
    runTask.includes('Г§ВЈВҒГ§вҖәЛңГ§В©ВәГ©вҖ”ВҙГӨВёВҚГЁВ¶ВіГҜВјЕ’ГҰвҖ”В ГҰВівҖўГ§В»В§Г§В»Вӯ OTA ГҰвҖәВҙГҰвҖ“В°') &&
    runTask.includes('runPostUpdateCleanup(backupPath)') &&
    runTask.includes('runFailedUpdateCleanup()') &&
    runTask.includes('cleanupOldReleases') &&
    runTask.includes('getRecentProtectedBackupPaths') &&
    runTask.includes('getCurrentReleaseTarget') &&
    runTask.includes('ГҘВ·ВІГҘЛҶВ Г©в„ўВӨГҰвҖ”В§ release') &&
    runTask.includes("'.incudal-update-downloads'") &&
    !runTask.includes("cp -a ${JSON.stringify(stagingDir)}/.") &&
    !runTask.includes("cp -a ${JSON.stringify(backupDir)}/.") &&
    runTask.includes('Auto rollback completed successfully') &&
    runTask.includes("status: rolledBack ? 'rolled_back' : 'failed'") &&
    runTask.includes('failed-update'),
  'online updater must prefer checksum-verified OTA release artifacts, support atomic current/release switching, clean OTA caches, preflight disk space, prune old releases safely, and preserve Git fallback mode'
)

assert.ok(
  runTask.includes("pnpm', ['install', '--prod', '--frozen-lockfile', '--force']") &&
    runTask.includes("timeoutMs: 600000,") &&
